            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="mb-0">Welcome to Mother Fit. We’re here to support you on your mental and physical journey throughout every stage of your pregnancy, postpartum and beyond. We offer a 360, holistic approach to motherhood. Looking after your mind, body and soul, we place an emphasis on all-round wellbeing, with the end result being a happier, healthier and more active you.</p>
