        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondTwo">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseBeyondTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBeyondTwo">What is the Mother Fit Rebuild your Core Program?</button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapseBeyondTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBeyondTwo" data-bs-parent="#BeyondAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="mb-0">The Mother Fit Rebuild your Core Program is recommended for any mother, no matter where you are in your motherhood journey.  You can start as soon as you feel ready after childbirth or years after having children. Every women can benefit from this program. This 6 step program is the foundations to rebuilding your core after pregnancy and can work alongside your women's physio recovery plan from diastasis recti if you have one.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondThree">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseBeyondThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBeyondThree">What is Mother Fit Beyond</button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapseBeyondThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBeyondThree" data-bs-parent="#BeyondAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>The team at Mother Fit knows the importance of carving out some much-needed ‘you’ time as a parent, which is why we have created our & Beyond program. Designed for women who are past the stages of pregnancy and postpartum, the program is an overall journey for an active and healthy lifestyle. Created for those wanting to develop their mind, body and soul. The Beyond program offers up to 6 live daily workouts or catch up on-demand at a time that suits you, challenges, and goal setting, yoga, meditation, breathwork and expert advisors. With a personalised dashboard bespoke to you, you’ll be able to access nutritional information, use a weight loss tracker, personalised calorie and information on what you’ve burnt, as well a photo and measurement tracker, daily step count and a sleep tracker.</p>
              <p>Disclaimer : Before commencing any new fitness, health, or nutrition program, please consult with your doctor to discuss your individual needs. I'm here to provide general advice within my scope of practice, but you should seek professional help if it is needed.</p>
              <p>If you're diabetic, have an injury or medical condition, Beyond/postpartum, or a physical disability, please consult your doctor or professional healthcare provider before starting.</p>
              <p>Always consult your healthcare professional before beginning any new exercise program, as there are some situations where exercise may not be advised.</p>
              <p class="mb-0">This information should be used as a guide only and should not replace the advice of your medical practitioner.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondFour">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseBeyondFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBeyondFour">What are Challenges?</button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapseBeyondFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBeyondFour" data-bs-parent="#BeyondAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="mb-0">Challenges run at ad hoc times of the year. However, you can always access previous challenges at a time that suits you from your dashboard.  Just follow the day by day plan within the challenge and you won't regret it. All of the challenges take a holistic approach to your wellbeing, not only including exercise, they provide advice from experts in many different fields of expertise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondFive">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseBeyondFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBeyondFive">What advice can I get on Nutrition?</button>
          </h3>
          <div id="collapseBeyondFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingBeyondFive" data-bs-parent="#BeyondAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p class="mb-0">I am a nutritional advisor for weight management and I use my years of working as a pre and postnatal trainer to advise on your pregnancy, postpartum and beyond nutritional needs. I don't believe in fad diets, Weight Watchers, Slimming World, I believe in educating women on food, taking it back to basics and getting whole foods with the right about for your energy demands. Oh and I love macros! So much so that I wrote a book in 2019 called 'What Would Mother Fit Eat?'. You can find an online version within the nutrition area on your dashboard. Start by reading my book and then progress onto one of the Ebook's and or a challenge.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondSix">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseBeyondSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseBeyondSix">What equipment do I need for workouts?</button>
