            <div class="accordion-body">
              <p>Find your tribe!!!</p>
              <p>Community and connectivity with women on the same journey as you is key to boosting your mood and alleviating any feelings of loneliness. This is why we are so proud of the private Mother Fit community we have created, where mums at every stage of their parenting journey come together to motivate and champion each other along the way. This group of women are passionate about building each other up and is a vital part of the Mother Fit program.  From sharing healthy recipes, top tips on how to get a baby to sleep, and advice on dealing with lack of sleep – the Mother Fit community is there. Surrounded by hundreds of like-minded women, you can find new friends, workout buddies and women to keep you accountable and on track.</p>
              <p class="mb-0">Access the Mother Fit private community here : <%= link_to "https://www.facebook.com/groups/840584283018084", "https://www.facebook.com/groups/840584283018084", rel: "noopener" %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingBeyondEight">
